it can be

31:03.680 --> 31:05.680
a change of the top manager team.

31:05.680 --> 31:07.680
But most often it is a process

31:07.680 --> 31:09.680
of merging and absorbing,

31:09.680 --> 31:11.680
rebranding,

31:11.680 --> 31:13.680
and in the situation when the company

31:13.680 --> 31:15.680
reaches a new quality level

31:15.680 --> 31:17.680
in some markets, including international.

31:18.040 --> 31:20.040
It is a very interesting experience

31:20.040 --> 31:22.040
of the company

31:22.040 --> 31:24.040
TNK BP,

31:24.040 --> 31:26.040
when the Russian company merged

31:26.040 --> 31:28.040
with the Western company.

31:30.040 --> 31:32.040
In order to understand

31:32.040 --> 31:34.040
what the corporate culture will be,

31:34.040 --> 31:36.040
the image of the

31:36.040 --> 31:38.040
single corporate culture was formed.

31:38.040 --> 31:40.040
It is clear that there were many nuances.

31:40.040 --> 31:42.040
On the one hand,

31:42.040 --> 31:44.040
the corporate culture of TNK

31:44.040 --> 31:46.040
was very different from the pro-Western style

31:46.400 --> 31:48.400
of work and interaction

31:48.400 --> 31:50.400
in the BP company.

31:50.400 --> 31:52.400
Moreover,

31:52.400 --> 31:54.400
there was a language barrier.

31:56.400 --> 31:58.400
The single-pronoun apparatus

31:58.400 --> 32:00.400
was complicated

32:00.400 --> 32:02.400
by the fact that people

32:02.400 --> 32:04.400
spoke different languages.

32:04.400 --> 32:06.400
TNK BP

32:06.400 --> 32:08.400
developed a huge number of programs

32:08.400 --> 32:10.400
in order to

32:10.400 --> 32:12.400
come to the new

32:12.400 --> 32:14.400
corporate culture

32:14.760 --> 32:16.760
that was formed

32:16.760 --> 32:18.760
at the stage of merging and absorbing.

32:18.760 --> 32:20.760
The company understood

32:20.760 --> 32:22.760
that there is a corporate culture

32:22.760 --> 32:24.760
of TNK,

32:24.760 --> 32:26.760
and there is a corporate culture of BP.

32:26.760 --> 32:28.760
And what kind of corporate culture

32:28.760 --> 32:30.760
we want to get.

32:30.760 --> 32:32.760
In the process of merging and absorbing

32:32.760 --> 32:34.760
there can be different interesting

32:34.760 --> 32:36.760
results.

32:36.760 --> 32:38.760
On the one hand,

32:38.760 --> 32:40.760
a stronger corporate culture

32:40.760 --> 32:42.760
can eat a weaker corporate culture.

32:43.120 --> 32:45.120
On the other hand,

32:45.120 --> 32:47.120
a new corporate culture

32:47.120 --> 32:49.120
can be created

32:49.120 --> 32:51.120
and the best

32:51.120 --> 32:53.120
of the two companies

32:53.120 --> 32:55.120
can be taken from the corporate culture

32:55.120 --> 32:57.120
of the other company.

32:57.120 --> 32:59.120
And a portrait of the company

32:59.120 --> 33:01.120
can be created.

33:01.120 --> 33:03.120
All the programs

33:03.120 --> 33:05.120
that are planned

33:05.120 --> 33:07.120
help to change

33:07.120 --> 33:09.120
the corporate culture

33:09.120 --> 33:11.120
of the company.

33:11.480 --> 33:13.480
For example,

33:13.480 --> 33:15.480
if the company

33:15.480 --> 33:17.480
lived in a conservative environment,

33:17.480 --> 33:19.480
the main postulate

33:19.480 --> 33:21.480
in the management style

33:21.480 --> 33:23.480
was an authoritarian style

33:23.480 --> 33:25.480
and a unilateral decision-making.

33:25.480 --> 33:27.480
And the company

33:27.480 --> 33:29.480
starts to make changes

33:29.480 --> 33:31.480
and understands

33:31.480 --> 33:33.480
that it hinders the company's development.

33:33.480 --> 33:35.480
It starts to change

33:35.480 --> 33:37.480
certain aspects of its approach.

33:37.480 --> 33:39.480
In particular,

33:39.840 --> 33:41.840
it helps to implement

33:41.840 --> 33:43.840
new modern tools,

33:43.840 --> 33:45.840
trends, approaches,

33:45.840 --> 33:47.840
motivation of the staff,

33:47.840 --> 33:49.840
interaction, decision-making.

33:49.840 --> 33:51.840
If a decision is made

33:51.840 --> 33:53.840
that we need to change

33:53.840 --> 33:55.840
the corporate management style

33:55.840 --> 33:57.840
and the management style

33:57.840 --> 33:59.840
of people

33:59.840 --> 34:01.840
to a more democratic plane,

34:01.840 --> 34:03.840
it is clear that

34:03.840 --> 34:05.840
the changes will not happen at once.

34:05.840 --> 34:07.840
Because the choice of the management style

34:08.200 --> 34:10.200
is a personal choice

34:10.200 --> 34:12.200
of the people

34:12.200 --> 34:14.200
who choose it.

34:14.200 --> 34:16.200
On the other hand,

34:16.200 --> 34:18.200
it is a norm

34:18.200 --> 34:20.200
that we are used to live in.

34:20.200 --> 34:22.200
It is hard to imagine

34:22.200 --> 34:24.200
that a person who interacted

34:24.200 --> 34:26.200
with a strict superordination

34:26.200 --> 34:28.200
will interact

34:28.200 --> 34:30.200
with a democratic one

34:30.200 --> 34:32.200
tomorrow.

34:32.200 --> 34:34.200
That is why

34:34.200 --> 34:36.200
a number of measures

34:36.560 --> 34:38.560
and projects

34:38.560 --> 34:40.560
are needed

34:40.560 --> 34:42.560
to make changes

34:42.560 --> 34:44.560
in people

34:44.560 --> 34:46.560
who are used

34:46.560 --> 34:48.560
to interact

34:48.560 --> 34:50.560
within the existing corporate culture.

34:52.560 --> 34:54.560
Let's go back to the situation

34:54.560 --> 34:56.560
when you are the initiator

34:56.560 --> 34:58.560
and you need to make an audit

34:58.560 --> 35:00.560
to understand

35:00.560 --> 35:02.560
the corporate culture.

35:02.560 --> 35:04.560
You decided to develop

35:04.920 --> 35:06.920
a project independently.

35:06.920 --> 35:08.920
How should it look like?

35:08.920 --> 35:10.920
It is a field of fantasy.

35:10.920 --> 35:12.920
It is important to remember

35:12.920 --> 35:14.920
that we ask any question

35:14.920 --> 35:16.920
with a goal

35:16.920 --> 35:18.920
to get a result.

35:18.920 --> 35:20.920
When you are forming this audit,

35:20.920 --> 35:22.920
base on these postulates.

35:22.920 --> 35:24.920
We form every question

35:24.920 --> 35:26.920
with a goal

35:26.920 --> 35:28.920
and we want

35:28.920 --> 35:30.920
to get a result.

35:30.920 --> 35:32.920
Then there will be no extra questions

35:33.280 --> 35:35.280
but the questions

35:35.280 --> 35:37.280
should cover

35:37.280 --> 35:39.280
the whole corporate culture.

35:39.280 --> 35:41.280
For example,

35:41.280 --> 35:43.280
you can form questions

35:43.280 --> 35:45.280
about your company's reputation

35:45.280 --> 35:47.280
as an employer,

35:47.280 --> 35:49.280
how the company is perceived

35:49.280 --> 35:51.280
as an attractive employer

35:51.280 --> 35:53.280
and not only

35:53.280 --> 35:55.280
by the employees

35:55.280 --> 35:57.280
who have been working for a long time

35:57.280 --> 35:59.280
but by all the employees

35:59.280 --> 36:01.280
including the new employees.

36:01.640 --> 36:03.640
You can ask questions

36:03.640 --> 36:05.640
about how your attitude

36:05.640 --> 36:07.640
to the company has changed

36:07.640 --> 36:09.640
before the company was created,

36:09.640 --> 36:11.640
during the adaptation period,

36:11.640 --> 36:13.640
during the working process

36:13.640 --> 36:15.640
and after 2-3 years

36:15.640 --> 36:17.640
if you have enough employees.

36:19.640 --> 36:21.640
The next thing

36:21.640 --> 36:23.640
that should be audited

36:23.640 --> 36:25.640
is the management style.

36:25.640 --> 36:27.640
What is the management style?

36:27.640 --> 36:29.640
There are many things

36:30.000 --> 36:32.000
that are connected to this.

36:32.000 --> 36:34.000
The decision-making,

36:34.000 --> 36:36.000
the communication,

36:36.000 --> 36:38.000
the business communication

36:38.000 --> 36:40.000
inside the company,

36:40.000 --> 36:42.000
the planning,

36:42.000 --> 36:44.000
the motivation system

36:44.000 --> 36:46.000
depend on the management style

36:46.000 --> 36:48.000
chosen by the company.

36:48.000 --> 36:50.000
The independence

36:50.000 --> 36:52.000
in the decision-making

36:52.000 --> 36:54.000
is also a component

36:54.000 --> 36:56.000
of the management style

36:56.000 --> 36:58.000
as well as the level of trust.

36:58.360 --> 37:00.360
It is based on the management

37:00.360 --> 37:02.360
of the people

37:02.360 --> 37:04.360
and the managerial competencies.

37:08.360 --> 37:10.360
You should also diagnose

37:10.360 --> 37:12.360
the innovation.

37:12.360 --> 37:14.360
How innovative the company is,

37:14.360 --> 37:16.360
how much the employees

37:16.360 --> 37:18.360
are used to living in the innovation,

37:18.360 --> 37:20.360
how much they are ready for changes,

37:20.360 --> 37:22.360
for the risk and so on.

37:22.360 --> 37:24.360
Another important factor

37:24.360 --> 37:26.360
is to determine

37:26.720 --> 37:28.720
how loyal the employees are

37:28.720 --> 37:30.720
to the company,

37:30.720 --> 37:32.720
how much they identify with the company,

37:32.720 --> 37:34.720
how much they value

37:34.720 --> 37:36.720
within the company

37:36.720 --> 37:38.720
and whether they think

37:38.720 --> 37:40.720
in the categories of business purpose.

37:40.720 --> 37:42.720
I call it the motive at the level of the idea.

37:42.720 --> 37:44.720
It is when any initiative,

37:44.720 --> 37:46.720
any action,

37:46.720 --> 37:48.720
any innovation

37:48.720 --> 37:50.720
is first of all measured

37:50.720 --> 37:52.720
on the business purpose,

37:52.720 --> 37:54.720
on the final business result.

37:55.080 --> 37:57.080
It is important to take a look

37:57.080 --> 37:59.080
at the workbook,

37:59.080 --> 38:01.080
to see Harrison's survey

38:01.080 --> 38:03.080
and to make an analysis

38:03.080 --> 38:05.080
of the corporate culture

38:05.080 --> 38:07.080
based on this survey.

38:15.080 --> 38:17.080
What happens

38:17.080 --> 38:19.080
in the situation of implementation

38:19.080 --> 38:21.080
of changes

38:21.080 --> 38:23.080
when we do not manage

38:23.440 --> 38:25.440
to follow the changes?

38:33.440 --> 38:35.440
Let's take a business process

38:35.440 --> 38:37.440
according to the scheme.

38:37.440 --> 38:39.440
The employees have a feeling

38:39.440 --> 38:41.440
that there is stability.

38:41.440 --> 38:43.440
They have stability.

38:43.440 --> 38:45.440
Most of the employees.

38:45.440 --> 38:47.440
The management of the company

38:47.440 --> 38:49.440
believes that the company

38:49.440 --> 38:51.440
needs to be brought to a new level.

38:51.800 --> 38:53.800
In fact, the changes are

38:53.800 --> 38:55.800
even the implementation

38:55.800 --> 38:57.800
of corporate standards.

38:57.800 --> 38:59.800
The company has been living

38:59.800 --> 39:01.800
without the standards of the external view

39:01.800 --> 39:03.800
and the standards of telecommunications.

39:05.800 --> 39:07.800
Tomorrow or in a week

39:07.800 --> 39:09.800
or sometime later

39:09.800 --> 39:11.800
the company introduces.

39:11.800 --> 39:13.800
The staff perceives it

39:13.800 --> 39:15.800
as a restriction of their freedom.

39:15.800 --> 39:17.800
I repeat,

39:17.800 --> 39:19.800
the normal reaction of the body

39:20.160 --> 39:22.160
is a change.

39:22.160 --> 39:24.160
We do not have any programs

39:24.160 --> 39:26.160
that would accompany

39:26.160 --> 39:28.160
these changes

39:28.160 --> 39:30.160
and contribute to the reduction

39:30.160 --> 39:32.160
of resistance.

39:32.160 --> 39:34.160
What happens?

39:34.160 --> 39:36.160
Stability, the feeling of the staff

39:36.160 --> 39:38.160
and the beginning of changes.

39:38.160 --> 39:40.160
Then the resistance begins.

39:40.160 --> 39:42.160
You continue to introduce changes.

39:42.160 --> 39:44.160
The resistance is intensified.

39:44.160 --> 39:46.160
Either in an open form,

39:46.160 --> 39:48.160
an open conflict,

39:48.520 --> 39:50.520
or in a hidden form,

39:50.520 --> 39:52.520
a hidden sabotage.

39:52.520 --> 39:54.520
What do you do next?

39:54.520 --> 39:56.520
You start to fight

39:56.520 --> 39:58.520
with these resistances.

39:58.520 --> 40:00.520
They do it in different ways.

40:00.520 --> 40:02.520
Sometimes they use administrative resources,

40:02.520 --> 40:04.520
administrative measures.

40:04.520 --> 40:06.520
Sometimes they try to clarify.

40:06.520 --> 40:08.520
But if your company

40:08.520 --> 40:10.520
is inclined to an authoritarian style of management,

40:10.520 --> 40:12.520
then most likely the clarification

40:12.520 --> 40:14.520
will have a declarative nature.

40:14.520 --> 40:16.520
It will look like

40:16.880 --> 40:18.880
you force your staff to be happy.

40:18.880 --> 40:20.880
They do not understand

40:20.880 --> 40:22.880
why they have to do this.

40:22.880 --> 40:24.880
They do not understand

40:24.880 --> 40:26.880
what is happening.

40:26.880 --> 40:28.880
Then there is

40:28.880 --> 40:30.880
either an exit from the change

40:30.880 --> 40:32.880
or the changes continue

40:32.880 --> 40:34.880
and you try to resist.

40:34.880 --> 40:36.880
What happens next?

40:36.880 --> 40:38.880
There is a destruction

40:38.880 --> 40:40.880
of a certain authenticity.

40:40.880 --> 40:42.880
When you have already

40:42.880 --> 40:44.880
come out of these changes,

40:45.240 --> 40:47.240
you can no longer live

40:47.240 --> 40:49.240
authentically as before.

40:49.240 --> 40:51.240
You can't live in a new way.

40:51.240 --> 40:53.240
You can't do it, you don't want to.

40:53.240 --> 40:55.240
Your staff is demotivated.

40:55.240 --> 40:57.240
Then there is

40:57.240 --> 40:59.240
a long process

40:59.240 --> 41:01.240
when you return to stability.

41:03.240 --> 41:05.240
Why do people resist changes?

41:05.240 --> 41:07.240
Because

41:07.240 --> 41:09.240
we are inclined

41:09.240 --> 41:11.240
to stability.

41:11.240 --> 41:13.240
The second step of the pyramid

41:13.600 --> 41:15.600
is the need for safety.

41:15.600 --> 41:17.600
For us, stability is a feeling of safety.

41:17.600 --> 41:19.600
It is a physiological need.

41:19.600 --> 41:21.600
We strive

41:21.600 --> 41:23.600
to surround and create

41:23.600 --> 41:25.600
a feeling of safety.

41:25.600 --> 41:27.600
If there are changes

41:27.600 --> 41:29.600
without accompaniment,

41:29.600 --> 41:31.600
without information,

41:31.600 --> 41:33.600
we resist.

41:33.600 --> 41:35.600
But when we do not receive information,

41:35.600 --> 41:37.600
what do we do?

41:37.600 --> 41:39.600
We think it over.

41:39.600 --> 41:41.600
We think it over

41:41.960 --> 41:43.960
and we are more likely

41:43.960 --> 41:45.960
to be disappointed.

41:45.960 --> 41:47.960
We expect negative changes

41:47.960 --> 41:49.960
rather than positive ones.

41:49.960 --> 41:51.960
This is a social and cultural feature

41:51.960 --> 41:53.960
of our country.

41:53.960 --> 41:55.960
The changes in our country

41:55.960 --> 41:57.960
were usually

41:57.960 --> 41:59.960
very encouraging

41:59.960 --> 42:01.960
and negative.

42:01.960 --> 42:03.960
We are all from the past life,

42:03.960 --> 42:05.960
from historical experience,

42:05.960 --> 42:07.960
from our own experience.

42:07.960 --> 42:09.960
We always expect something bad.

42:10.320 --> 42:12.320
We always

42:12.320 --> 42:14.320
evaluate changes

42:14.320 --> 42:16.320
in the situation

42:16.320 --> 42:18.320
that will bring

42:18.320 --> 42:20.320
positive changes

42:20.320 --> 42:22.320
to me.

42:22.320 --> 42:24.320
Every time we combine

42:24.320 --> 42:26.320
our goals and motives

42:26.320 --> 42:28.320
with the changes

42:28.320 --> 42:30.320
that are happening.

42:30.320 --> 42:32.320
There are changes in goals,

42:32.320 --> 42:34.320
motives, values.

42:34.320 --> 42:36.320
And every time a person evaluates

42:36.320 --> 42:38.320
the changes that will come

42:38.680 --> 42:40.680
and contribute

42:40.680 --> 42:42.680
to his goals.

42:42.680 --> 42:44.680
And how much

42:44.680 --> 42:46.680
the goals that will be within the company

42:46.680 --> 42:48.680
correspond to his goals, motives,

42:48.680 --> 42:50.680
values.

42:50.680 --> 42:52.680
If he does not receive information,

42:52.680 --> 42:54.680
he begins to resist it.

42:54.680 --> 42:56.680
Because it is a threat

42:56.680 --> 42:58.680
to his safety,

42:58.680 --> 43:00.680
his personality

43:00.680 --> 43:02.680
and values.

43:02.680 --> 43:04.680
A person perceives it this way.

43:04.680 --> 43:06.680
Now let's look at the situation

43:07.040 --> 43:09.040
where the company culture

43:09.040 --> 43:11.040
is being accompanied.

43:11.040 --> 43:13.040
The situation again.

43:13.040 --> 43:15.040
The feeling of stability

43:15.040 --> 43:17.040
of the staff.

43:17.040 --> 43:19.040
Then preparation

43:19.040 --> 43:21.040
for the changes begins.

43:21.040 --> 43:23.040
It begins with an analysis

43:23.040 --> 43:25.040
of the existing corporate culture.

43:25.040 --> 43:27.040
Including understanding

43:27.040 --> 43:29.040
how much the corporate culture

43:29.040 --> 43:31.040
will contribute, help with the changes.

43:31.040 --> 43:33.040
How much it will interfere with these changes.

43:33.040 --> 43:35.040
Then the vision is formed

43:35.400 --> 43:37.400
or the corporate culture

43:37.400 --> 43:39.400
that we want to come to.

43:39.400 --> 43:41.400
In all its components.

43:41.400 --> 43:43.400
And,

43:43.400 --> 43:45.400
based on this,

43:45.400 --> 43:47.400
certain approaches are formed

43:47.400 --> 43:49.400
in terms of how to motivate the staff.

43:49.400 --> 43:51.400
How to form

43:51.400 --> 43:53.400
the staff's

43:53.400 --> 43:55.400
commitment to the changes.

43:55.400 --> 43:57.400
How to involve the staff

43:57.400 --> 43:59.400
in the process of change.

43:59.400 --> 44:01.400
What to do

44:01.400 --> 44:03.400
so that people

44:03.760 --> 44:05.760
participate in these changes.

44:05.760 --> 44:07.760
So that they accept them

44:07.760 --> 44:09.760
and, most importantly,

44:09.760 --> 44:11.760
do not resist these changes.

44:11.760 --> 44:13.760
In fact,

44:13.760 --> 44:15.760
the search begins

44:15.760 --> 44:17.760
in the process of adaptation.

44:17.760 --> 44:19.760
The adaptation of people

44:19.760 --> 44:21.760
to the changes

44:21.760 --> 44:23.760
of the corporate culture.

44:23.760 --> 44:25.760
Sometimes,

44:25.760 --> 44:27.760
in the situation of changes,

44:27.760 --> 44:29.760
including at the stage of preparation,

44:29.760 --> 44:31.760
the agents of changes are determined.

44:32.120 --> 44:34.120
A model of competence

44:34.120 --> 44:36.120
for these agents of changes is formed.

44:36.120 --> 44:38.120
These people are identified

44:38.120 --> 44:40.120
who will help the management,

44:40.120 --> 44:42.120
help the company

44:42.120 --> 44:44.120
implement these changes.

44:44.120 --> 44:46.120
They can be informal leaders.

44:46.120 --> 44:48.120
They can be formal leaders,

44:48.120 --> 44:50.120
that is, the existing managers of the management link.

44:50.120 --> 44:52.120
And they actively

44:52.120 --> 44:54.120
draft and implement

44:54.120 --> 44:56.120
in addition to the existing programs

44:56.120 --> 44:58.120
in the company

44:58.120 --> 45:00.120
some new standards

45:00.480 --> 45:02.480
of behavior, interaction

45:02.480 --> 45:04.480
that will occur

45:04.480 --> 45:06.480
as a result of the changes

45:06.480 --> 45:08.480
that will be present in the company.

45:08.480 --> 45:10.480
Actually,

45:10.480 --> 45:12.480
this path can take

45:12.480 --> 45:14.480
quite a long time.

45:14.480 --> 45:16.480
In particular, the same company,

45:16.480 --> 45:18.480
TNK-BP,

45:18.480 --> 45:20.480
has been implementing the process

45:20.480 --> 45:22.480
of changing the corporate culture for four years.

45:22.480 --> 45:24.480
And in the next three or four years,

45:24.480 --> 45:26.480
they are planning programs

