59:21.160 --> 59:23.160
that will help

59:23.160 --> 59:25.160
to identify

59:25.160 --> 59:27.160
the employees

59:27.160 --> 59:29.160
from the company

59:29.160 --> 59:31.160
and, as a result,

59:31.160 --> 59:33.160
to achieve the business goals.

59:33.160 --> 59:35.160
The corporate university

59:35.160 --> 59:37.160
is a tool of corporate management

59:37.160 --> 59:39.160
to realize

59:39.160 --> 59:41.160
the strategic goals of the company.

59:41.160 --> 59:43.160
There are a lot

59:43.160 --> 59:45.160
of corporate universities

59:45.160 --> 59:47.160
in Russia.

59:47.160 --> 59:49.160
Unfortunately,

59:49.160 --> 59:51.160
not all of them are Russian.

59:51.160 --> 59:53.160
Sometimes they are just

59:53.160 --> 59:55.160
educational centers,

59:55.160 --> 59:57.160
either internal or external.

59:57.160 --> 59:59.160
They don't solve the ideological task

59:59.160 --> 01:00:01.160
or don't solve it at all.

01:00:01.160 --> 01:00:03.160
But from the point of view

01:00:03.160 --> 01:00:05.160
of the Western standards,

01:00:05.160 --> 01:00:07.160
the corporate university

01:00:07.160 --> 01:00:09.160
solves the main task

01:00:09.160 --> 01:00:11.160
in creating the ideology

01:00:11.160 --> 01:00:13.160
and forming the loyalty

01:00:13.160 --> 01:00:15.160
of the company.

01:00:15.160 --> 01:00:17.160
I told you about the Beeline experience.

01:00:17.160 --> 01:00:19.160
Many Russian companies

01:00:19.160 --> 01:00:21.160
are implementing the same changes.

01:00:21.160 --> 01:00:23.160
The experience of the Western companies

01:00:23.160 --> 01:00:25.160
is very interesting.

01:00:25.160 --> 01:00:27.160
The company called

01:00:27.160 --> 01:00:29.160
Walt Disney

01:00:29.160 --> 01:00:31.160
tried to preserve

01:00:31.160 --> 01:00:33.160
the dying corporate culture.

01:00:33.160 --> 01:00:35.160
Because after Walt Disney's death,

01:00:35.160 --> 01:00:37.160
the standards he created

01:00:37.160 --> 01:00:39.160
were not

01:00:39.160 --> 01:00:41.160
in the same place

01:00:41.160 --> 01:00:43.160
as the current one.

01:00:43.160 --> 01:00:45.160
The company

01:00:45.160 --> 01:00:47.160
Walt Disney

01:00:47.160 --> 01:00:49.160
was innovative

01:00:49.160 --> 01:00:51.160
and constantly changing.

01:00:51.160 --> 01:00:53.160
Moreover, Walt Disney

01:00:53.160 --> 01:00:55.160
is the person

01:00:55.160 --> 01:00:57.160
who created

01:00:57.160 --> 01:00:59.160
certain approaches

01:00:59.160 --> 01:01:01.160
to the management of changes.

01:01:01.160 --> 01:01:03.160
For example,

01:01:03.160 --> 01:01:05.160
he had three groups.

01:01:05.160 --> 01:01:07.160
The first group was

01:01:07.160 --> 01:01:09.160
the ideologists and creatives.

01:01:09.160 --> 01:01:11.160
They were creating the ideas.

01:01:11.160 --> 01:01:13.160
The third group

01:01:13.160 --> 01:01:15.160
was the people who criticized

01:01:15.160 --> 01:01:17.160
the ideas and took risks.

01:01:17.160 --> 01:01:19.160
Then the ideas were finalized.

01:01:19.160 --> 01:01:21.160
After the finalization,

01:01:21.160 --> 01:01:23.160
the third group of the creators

01:01:23.160 --> 01:01:25.160
was the ones who implemented

01:01:25.160 --> 01:01:27.160
the ideas.

01:01:27.160 --> 01:01:29.160
Thus, Walt Disney's company

01:01:29.160 --> 01:01:31.160
was developing and new products

01:01:31.160 --> 01:01:33.160
were coming.

01:01:33.160 --> 01:01:35.160
The new products of Walt Disney

01:01:35.160 --> 01:01:37.160
are the cartoons we watch.

01:01:37.160 --> 01:01:39.160
When Walt Disney died,

01:01:39.160 --> 01:01:41.160
the company lost

01:01:41.160 --> 01:01:43.160
its standards

01:01:43.160 --> 01:01:45.160
and innovation.

01:01:45.160 --> 01:01:47.160
Then the corporate university

01:01:47.160 --> 01:01:49.160
was created.

01:01:49.160 --> 01:01:51.160
It was created to

01:01:51.160 --> 01:01:53.160
constantly support the company

01:01:53.160 --> 01:01:55.160
in the process of changes

01:01:55.160 --> 01:01:57.160
and to preserve

01:01:57.160 --> 01:01:59.160
the standards and ideological postulates

01:01:59.160 --> 01:02:01.160
and to multiply

01:02:01.160 --> 01:02:03.160
and give the opportunity

01:02:03.160 --> 01:02:05.160
to the company to develop further.

01:02:05.160 --> 01:02:07.160
This is a very interesting experience

01:02:07.160 --> 01:02:09.160
of the Western companies.

01:02:11.160 --> 01:02:13.160
Another distinctive feature

01:02:13.160 --> 01:02:15.160
of the corporate universities

01:02:15.160 --> 01:02:17.160
is that the corporate universities

01:02:17.160 --> 01:02:19.160
are the internal lecturers.

01:02:19.160 --> 01:02:21.160
They are the top managers of the companies.

01:02:21.160 --> 01:02:23.160
They are actively involved in this.

01:02:23.160 --> 01:02:25.160
It is clear that the initiators

01:02:25.160 --> 01:02:27.160
of any global changes

01:02:27.160 --> 01:02:29.160
are the managers.

01:02:29.160 --> 01:02:31.160
Moreover, the success of changes

01:02:31.160 --> 01:02:33.160
increases when

01:02:33.160 --> 01:02:35.160
the leaders are the initiators.

01:02:35.160 --> 01:02:37.160
They are actively involved in this.

01:02:37.160 --> 01:02:39.160
That is why the ideology

01:02:39.160 --> 01:02:41.160
is formed in the heads

01:02:41.160 --> 01:02:43.160
and the ideology is mostly

01:02:43.160 --> 01:02:45.160
printed on the top.

01:02:45.160 --> 01:02:47.160
That is why the top managers

01:02:47.160 --> 01:02:49.160
are the internal lecturers

01:02:49.160 --> 01:02:51.160
of the corporate universities.

01:02:51.160 --> 01:02:53.160
This is a distinctive feature

01:02:53.160 --> 01:02:55.160
of the corporate universities,

01:02:55.160 --> 01:02:57.160
especially of the Western and Russian ones.

01:02:57.160 --> 01:02:59.160
Also, within the framework

01:02:59.160 --> 01:03:01.160
of the corporate universities

01:03:01.160 --> 01:03:03.160
the values are transmitted

01:03:03.160 --> 01:03:05.160
from the old employees

01:03:05.160 --> 01:03:07.160
to the new ones.

01:03:07.160 --> 01:03:09.160
They are multiplied

01:03:09.160 --> 01:03:11.160
and preserved.

01:03:11.160 --> 01:03:13.160
How and what tools

01:03:13.160 --> 01:03:15.160
should be used

01:03:15.160 --> 01:03:17.160
to form the corporate culture

01:03:17.160 --> 01:03:19.160
of remote, isolated offices

01:03:19.160 --> 01:03:21.160
or virtual offices?

01:03:21.160 --> 01:03:23.160
I will not talk about

01:03:23.160 --> 01:03:25.160
the corporate universities

01:03:25.160 --> 01:03:27.160
because all employees

01:03:27.160 --> 01:03:29.160
are trained there.

01:03:29.160 --> 01:03:31.160
The first step is

01:03:31.160 --> 01:03:33.160
to enter the company

01:03:33.160 --> 01:03:35.160
through the corporate universities,

01:03:35.160 --> 01:03:37.160
to learn and to learn

01:03:37.160 --> 01:03:39.160
about the values, standards

01:03:39.160 --> 01:03:41.160
and missions.

01:03:41.160 --> 01:03:43.160
How to support?

01:03:43.160 --> 01:03:45.160
It is clear that you can support

01:03:45.160 --> 01:03:47.160
only through the constant

01:03:47.160 --> 01:03:49.160
communication and interaction.

01:03:49.160 --> 01:03:51.160
Regular meetings,

01:03:51.160 --> 01:03:53.160
video conferences,

01:03:53.160 --> 01:03:55.160
regular communication

01:03:55.160 --> 01:03:57.160
and information about

01:03:57.160 --> 01:03:59.160
the changes in the company,

01:03:59.160 --> 01:04:01.160
discussions,

01:04:01.160 --> 01:04:03.160
regular interaction

01:04:03.160 --> 01:04:05.160
in the online mode.

01:04:05.160 --> 01:04:07.160
There should not be a situation

01:04:07.160 --> 01:04:09.160
where the isolated structures

01:04:09.160 --> 01:04:11.160
live their own life

01:04:11.160 --> 01:04:13.160
and the head office lives its own.

01:04:13.160 --> 01:04:15.160
As soon as such a situation arises,

01:04:15.160 --> 01:04:17.160
there is a serious danger

01:04:17.160 --> 01:04:19.160
that the isolated structures

01:04:19.160 --> 01:04:21.160
will form their own subculture

01:04:21.160 --> 01:04:23.160
which is not a fact

01:04:23.160 --> 01:04:25.160
and will be congruent

01:04:25.160 --> 01:04:27.160
to the corporate culture

01:04:27.160 --> 01:04:29.160
of the head office.

01:04:29.160 --> 01:04:31.160
Then you may face

01:04:31.160 --> 01:04:33.160
serious problems.

01:04:33.160 --> 01:04:35.160
Formalized things are used,

01:04:35.160 --> 01:04:37.160
the corporate code,

01:04:37.160 --> 01:04:39.160
which is used to register

01:04:39.160 --> 01:04:41.160
all the things,

01:04:41.160 --> 01:04:43.160
all the standards, values,

01:04:43.160 --> 01:04:45.160
missions, standards of work,

01:04:45.160 --> 01:04:47.160
standards of interaction,

01:04:47.160 --> 01:04:49.160
standards of appearance,

01:04:49.160 --> 01:04:51.160
all the algorithms,

01:04:51.160 --> 01:04:53.160
organizational structure,

01:04:53.160 --> 01:04:55.160
which are related to the corporate culture.

01:04:55.160 --> 01:04:57.160
Traditions are also introduced

01:04:57.160 --> 01:04:59.160
through rituals.

01:04:59.160 --> 01:05:01.160
For example,

01:05:01.160 --> 01:05:03.160
rituals of promotion,

01:05:03.160 --> 01:05:05.160
rituals of movement,

01:05:05.160 --> 01:05:07.160
rituals of reception to work,

01:05:07.160 --> 01:05:09.160
rituals of resolving conflicts

01:05:09.160 --> 01:05:11.160
and so on.

01:05:11.160 --> 01:05:13.160
I repeat that one of the tools

01:05:13.160 --> 01:05:15.160
that forms the corporate culture

01:05:15.160 --> 01:05:17.160
and informs about the standards

01:05:17.160 --> 01:05:19.160
that exist in the company

01:05:19.160 --> 01:05:21.160
is the corporate code of the company.

01:05:21.160 --> 01:05:23.160
The corporate code,

01:05:23.160 --> 01:05:25.160
as I said, includes

01:05:25.160 --> 01:05:27.160
almost all elements,

01:05:27.160 --> 01:05:29.160
but the components of the corporate code

01:05:29.160 --> 01:05:31.160
look like this.

01:05:31.160 --> 01:05:33.160
These are some basic principles of work,

01:05:33.160 --> 01:05:35.160
values and standards of behavior.

01:05:35.160 --> 01:05:37.160
Actually,

01:05:37.160 --> 01:05:39.160
it is filled with the content.

01:05:41.160 --> 01:05:43.160
Some time ago,

01:05:43.160 --> 01:05:45.160
when we were studying

01:05:45.160 --> 01:05:47.160
with an American professor,

01:05:47.160 --> 01:05:49.160
I asked how the corporate code

01:05:49.160 --> 01:05:51.160
looks like in the USA.

01:05:51.160 --> 01:05:53.160
I was told that the corporate code

01:05:53.160 --> 01:05:55.160
in the USA looks like a thick

01:05:55.160 --> 01:05:57.160
big piece of paper

01:05:57.160 --> 01:05:59.160
in which everything is

01:05:59.160 --> 01:06:01.160
formalized and prescribed.

01:06:01.160 --> 01:06:03.160
Starting with the mission of values,

01:06:03.160 --> 01:06:05.160
as I said,

01:06:05.160 --> 01:06:07.160
continuing with the organizational structure,

01:06:07.160 --> 01:06:09.160
including the faces of the first people,

01:06:09.160 --> 01:06:11.160
their experience of work,

01:06:11.160 --> 01:06:13.160
their life path,

01:06:13.160 --> 01:06:15.160
then the standards of behavior,

01:06:15.160 --> 01:06:17.160
standards of interaction,

01:06:17.160 --> 01:06:19.160
in particular, if the company is engaged in sales,

01:06:19.160 --> 01:06:21.160
then in this corporate code

01:06:23.160 --> 01:06:25.160
everything related to sales

01:06:25.160 --> 01:06:27.160
is prescribed and standardized.

01:06:27.160 --> 01:06:29.160
But this is a fairly living tool.

01:06:31.160 --> 01:06:33.160
Moreover,

01:06:33.160 --> 01:06:35.160
considering the fact that the West

01:06:35.160 --> 01:06:37.160
has gone far enough,

01:06:37.160 --> 01:06:39.160
and there are usually electronic documents in companies,

01:06:39.160 --> 01:06:41.160
on the contrary,

01:06:41.160 --> 01:06:43.160
employees are not given

01:06:43.160 --> 01:06:45.160
this corporate code,

01:06:45.160 --> 01:06:47.160
but are given a hard drive,

01:06:47.160 --> 01:06:49.160
or they are used as a common resource

01:06:49.160 --> 01:06:51.160
where they can be familiarized.

01:06:51.160 --> 01:06:53.160
Certain programs are formed,

01:06:53.160 --> 01:06:55.160
which control,

01:06:55.160 --> 01:06:57.160
either teach people through education,

01:06:57.160 --> 01:06:59.160
or control the study of corporate standards.

01:06:59.160 --> 01:07:01.160
Then people go through the assessment

01:07:01.160 --> 01:07:03.160
of whether they understood

01:07:03.160 --> 01:07:05.160
what is written in this corporate code.

01:07:07.160 --> 01:07:09.160
So,

01:07:09.160 --> 01:07:11.160
this document is quite alive.

01:07:11.160 --> 01:07:13.160
The professor I was studying with

01:07:13.160 --> 01:07:15.160
said that if something new

01:07:15.160 --> 01:07:17.160
appears in a company,

01:07:17.160 --> 01:07:19.160
or a response to an objection,

01:07:19.160 --> 01:07:21.160
or a resolution of a conflict,

01:07:21.160 --> 01:07:23.160
then it is immediately placed

01:07:23.160 --> 01:07:25.160
in the corporate code.

01:07:25.160 --> 01:07:27.160
If something changes,

01:07:27.160 --> 01:07:29.160
the structure changes,

01:07:29.160 --> 01:07:31.160
it is immediately changed in the corporate code.

01:07:31.160 --> 01:07:33.160
This is an absolutely living document.

01:07:33.160 --> 01:07:35.160
It lives together with the company.

01:07:35.160 --> 01:07:37.160
It does not live separately from the company.

01:07:37.160 --> 01:07:39.160
This is very important to understand.

01:07:39.160 --> 01:07:41.160
Because,

01:07:41.160 --> 01:07:43.160
unfortunately,

01:07:43.160 --> 01:07:45.160
sometimes managers and

01:07:45.160 --> 01:07:47.160
personnel specialists

01:07:47.160 --> 01:07:49.160
think that they have

01:07:49.160 --> 01:07:51.160
created this document,

01:07:51.160 --> 01:07:53.160
put it on the shelf,

01:07:53.160 --> 01:07:55.160
and that's it.

01:07:55.160 --> 01:07:57.160
In the best case,

01:07:57.160 --> 01:07:59.160
they have created an education system

01:07:59.160 --> 01:08:01.160
at the stage of joining a company.

01:08:01.160 --> 01:08:03.160
For beginners.

01:08:03.160 --> 01:08:05.160
This is not so.

01:08:05.160 --> 01:08:07.160
This document must be alive.

01:08:07.160 --> 01:08:09.160
It must live with the company.

01:08:09.160 --> 01:08:11.160
It contributes,

01:08:11.160 --> 01:08:13.160
but also prevents

01:08:13.160 --> 01:08:15.160
changes in corporate culture,

01:08:15.160 --> 01:08:17.160
and, in particular,

01:08:17.160 --> 01:08:19.160
changes in the company.

01:08:19.160 --> 01:08:21.160
What is it?

01:08:21.160 --> 01:08:23.160
First of all,

01:08:23.160 --> 01:08:25.160
it is a lack of development strategy.

01:08:25.160 --> 01:08:27.160
Next, it is a substitution of the process

01:08:27.160 --> 01:08:29.160
of changing culture of advertising

01:08:29.160 --> 01:08:31.160
or new jargon.

01:08:31.160 --> 01:08:33.160
This often happens when rebranding happens.

01:08:33.160 --> 01:08:35.160
Moreover,

01:08:35.160 --> 01:08:37.160
sometimes consultants

01:08:37.160 --> 01:08:39.160
do rebranding

01:08:39.160 --> 01:08:41.160
when they join a company.

01:08:41.160 --> 01:08:43.160
In order to get rid of taxes

01:08:43.160 --> 01:08:45.160
or to make some changes.

01:08:45.160 --> 01:08:47.160
Because sometimes

01:08:47.160 --> 01:08:49.160
the sign changes,

01:08:49.160 --> 01:08:51.160
the facade changes,

01:08:51.160 --> 01:08:53.160
but nothing changes

01:08:53.160 --> 01:08:55.160
behind this facade.

01:08:55.160 --> 01:08:57.160
This is a substitution.

01:08:57.160 --> 01:08:59.160
Substitution of changes.

01:08:59.160 --> 01:09:01.160
It is clear that people

01:09:01.160 --> 01:09:03.160
will not believe in

01:09:03.160 --> 01:09:05.160
the leadership

01:09:05.160 --> 01:09:07.160
that will declare

01:09:07.160 --> 01:09:09.160
that changes will be made

01:09:09.160 --> 01:09:11.160
after brand change.

01:09:11.160 --> 01:09:13.160
This will not contribute

01:09:13.160 --> 01:09:15.160
to the efficiency of the company.

01:09:17.160 --> 01:09:19.160
What else is a hindrance?

01:09:19.160 --> 01:09:21.160
In particular,

01:09:21.160 --> 01:09:23.160
initiating changes from the middle level.

01:09:23.160 --> 01:09:25.160
Any global changes

01:09:25.160 --> 01:09:27.160
must be initiated from the top level.

01:09:27.160 --> 01:09:29.160
In particular, changes that bring

01:09:29.160 --> 01:09:31.160
changes to the corporate culture of the company.

01:09:31.160 --> 01:09:33.160
This does not mean that you should not be

01:09:33.160 --> 01:09:35.160
involved in the implementation of a project.

01:09:35.160 --> 01:09:37.160
You should be involved in the implementation

01:09:37.160 --> 01:09:39.160
of something new.

01:09:39.160 --> 01:09:41.160
Moreover,

01:09:41.160 --> 01:09:43.160
you should assess

01:09:43.160 --> 01:09:45.160
how the projects you will implement

01:09:45.160 --> 01:09:47.160
will contribute to the improvement of the company.

01:09:47.160 --> 01:09:49.160
And how much the existing corporate culture

01:09:49.160 --> 01:09:51.160
will interfere or not.

01:09:51.160 --> 01:09:53.160
Global changes,

01:09:53.160 --> 01:09:55.160
changes that attract the value level,

01:09:55.160 --> 01:09:57.160
attract the strategy of the company,

01:09:57.160 --> 01:09:59.160
are initiated by the top management.

01:09:59.160 --> 01:10:01.160
And then these changes

01:10:01.160 --> 01:10:03.160
are much more effective.

01:10:03.160 --> 01:10:05.160
What else is a hindrance?

01:10:05.160 --> 01:10:07.160
When short-term goals dominate.

01:10:07.160 --> 01:10:09.160
When we live with some

01:10:09.160 --> 01:10:11.160
minute needs,

01:10:11.160 --> 01:10:13.160
we do not think and do not think

01:10:13.160 --> 01:10:15.160
about the long-term prospects.

01:10:15.160 --> 01:10:17.160
There is a strategic planning

01:10:17.160 --> 01:10:19.160
and strategic goals.

01:10:19.160 --> 01:10:21.160
And, in fact,

01:10:21.160 --> 01:10:23.160
according to the same

01:10:23.160 --> 01:10:25.160
Franklin's Pyramid,

01:10:25.160 --> 01:10:27.160
long-term goals follow

01:10:27.160 --> 01:10:29.160
the most important goals.

01:10:29.160 --> 01:10:31.160
When we think about the minute,

01:10:31.160 --> 01:10:33.160
we do not think about the day after.

01:10:33.160 --> 01:10:35.160
We lose much more than when we think

01:10:35.160 --> 01:10:37.160
about the long-term prospects

01:10:37.160 --> 01:10:39.160
and global things.

01:10:39.160 --> 01:10:41.160
And one more obstacle.

01:10:41.160 --> 01:10:43.160
Cynicism as a consequence

01:10:43.160 --> 01:10:45.160
of the lack of value.

01:10:45.160 --> 01:10:47.160
Cynicism is, in principle,

01:10:47.160 --> 01:10:49.160
the lack of values.

01:10:49.160 --> 01:10:51.160
It is clear that

01:10:51.160 --> 01:10:53.160
cynics probably also have some values.

01:10:53.160 --> 01:10:55.160
But to a greater extent,

01:10:55.160 --> 01:10:57.160
