01:27:05.160 --> 01:27:07.160
What conclusions can be drawn?

01:27:07.160 --> 01:27:09.160
A corporate culture

01:27:09.160 --> 01:27:11.160
is not bad or good.

01:27:11.160 --> 01:27:13.160
It can be appropriate.

01:27:13.160 --> 01:27:15.160
A corporate culture

01:27:15.160 --> 01:27:17.160
or even a subculture

01:27:17.160 --> 01:27:19.160
can be a catalyst

01:27:19.160 --> 01:27:21.160
for the change.

01:27:21.160 --> 01:27:23.160
It can slow down the change.

01:27:23.160 --> 01:27:25.160
Reforming a corporate culture

01:27:25.160 --> 01:27:27.160
is a long and complex process

01:27:27.160 --> 01:27:29.160
that takes a long time.

01:27:31.160 --> 01:27:33.160
You should approach this process

01:27:33.160 --> 01:27:35.160
responsibly,

01:27:35.160 --> 01:27:37.160
consciously and planarly.

